## Description

Overlapping histograms allow us to compare distributions across the groups of a categorical (or ordinal) variable.

## Set up

:::: {.panel-tabset}



::: {style="font-size: 1.15em; color: #1e83c8;"}
**PACKAGES:**
:::

::: {style="font-size: 0.85em;"}
Install packages.
:::


::: {style="font-size: 0.75em;"}

::: {.cell}

